text: So manga rrzik a manga babay na pantag a manga rrzik a manga mama, go so manga rrzik a manga mama na pantag o manga rrzik a manga babay, na so manga soti a manga babay na pantag o manga soti a manga mama, go so manga soti a manga mama a pantag o manga soti a manga babay: Siran man na di masosogat o katharo iran (a kabokhag): adn a bagian iran a maap, go pagpr a mapiya
